" Quick jump to first item starting with X
function! s:NERDJump(search, backwards)
    if a:backwards
        :silent! :exe '?\s\+\<'.a:search
    else
        :silent! :exe '/\s\+\<'.a:search
    end 
endfunction
command! -nargs=* NERDJump call s:NERDJump(<f-args>)

